-- Argentina's Pan American Energy Plans Sale of $500 Million Bonds Due 2021
-- Drew Benson
-- 2010-04-23T18:30:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/argentina-s-pan-american-energy-plans-sale-of-500-million-bonds-due-2021.html

          
          
              Pan American Energy LLC, the
Argentine unit of London-based BP Plc, approved the sale of as
much as $500 million worth of international bonds that mature in
2021 to fund investments and refinancing, the company said in a
filing today with Argentine regulators.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Drew Benson in Buenos Aires at 
 abenson9@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        